OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fbreezy overnight, especially in the
OL,7,Fwest. Showers will become less
OL,8,Ffrequent, but persist overnight,
OL,9,Fparticularly near eastern and western
OL,10,Fcoasts. Some inland areas becoming dry
OL,11,Fwith clear spells. Chilly, but mostly
OL,12,Ffrost free.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,15,Fand scattered showers, heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery at times, especially in the
OL,17,Fsouth. Drier in central areas. Feeling
OL,18,Frather chilly in the brisk northerly
OL,19,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
